---
title: Pan-Roasted Salmon with Mustard-Butter Bean Salad
description: This recipe is all about contrast - creamy butter beans, crisp snap peas, tangy mustard, and earthy coriander guarantee your tastebuds won't be bored. Lemon and butter-basted salmon is the crowning glory to this restaurant-worthy dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54e492646ced6e474a8b456a.jpg
